## What This Module Does

This module ports the "Depth Contour Datamosh" effect from VJlive-2. It extracts iso-depth contour lines from the depth map (like elevation lines on a map) and concentrates datamosh/glitch artifacts specifically along these contour boundaries. The result is a topographic "layer cake" corruption where each depth slice glitches independently.

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- It does NOT rely on motion estimation vectors (it derives its displacement purely from spatial gradients in the depth map).
- It does NOT use a secondary video feed for motion (it uses the depth map as the motion driver).

