---

## Edge Cases and Error Handling

- **Missing Depth Input**: Bypasses the datamosh and contour extraction, outputting `video_in` directly (SAFETY RAIL #7).
- **FBO Cleanup**: As a datamosh effect, it requires a feedback FBO (`texPrev`) which must be explicitly cleaned up on unload (SAFETY RAIL #8).
- **Performance Budget**: Gradient calculation (Sobel filter equivalent) for contour extraction must be optimized in the fragment shader to avoid breaking the 60 FPS limit (SAFETY RAIL #1).

